        <oboInOwl:inSubset rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/uberon/core#human_reference_atlas"/>
        <rdfs:comment>This term applies to metazoan. For plant stem cells, consider using PO:0004011 ‘initial cell’ or its parent PO:0004010 ‘meristematic cell’.</rdfs:comment>
