        <oboInOwl:inSubset rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/go#goslim_plant"/>
        <rdfs:comment>The outer membrane (of gram negative bacteria) or cell wall (of yeast or Gram positive bacteria) are defined as parts of this structure, see &apos;external encapsulating structure part&apos;.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>external encapsulating structure</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
