        <owl:annotatedTarget>A transparent and refractive lens located posterior to the iris. The lens of camera-type eye refracts light to be focused on the retina.</owl:annotatedTarget>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>Wikipedia:Lens_(anatomy)</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
