        <owl:annotatedProperty rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBPROP_0000011"/>
        <owl:annotatedTarget>The mature structure of the neural tube exists when the tube has been segmented into the forebrain, midbrain, hindbrain and spinal cord regions. In addition neural crest has budded away from the epithelium</owl:annotatedTarget>
        <oboInOwl:source>GO:0021915</oboInOwl:source>
