            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>The space in the eye, filled with aqueous humor, and bounded anteriorly by the cornea and a small portion of the sclera and posteriorly by a small portion of the ciliary body, the iris, and part of the crystalline lens.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:UBPROP_0000001>The part of the eyeball between the cornea and the iris, filled with aqueous humor. [TFD][VHOG]</obo:UBPROP_0000001>
        <obo:UBPROP_0000012>space in EHDAA2 - consider adding Cavity of anterior chamber of eyeball</obo:UBPROP_0000012>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>BTO:0002084</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
        <oboInOwl:hasDbXref>EHDAA2:0000129</oboInOwl:hasDbXref>
