        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:nodeID="genid1912"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A layer of epithelium that lines the heart, blood vessels (endothelium, vascular), lymph vessels (endothelium, lymphatic), and the serous cavities of the body[MESH]. Simple squamous epithelium which lines blood and lymphatic vessels and the heart[FMA].</obo:IAO_0000115>
