        <oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>uberon</oboInOwl:hasOBONamespace>
        <oboInOwl:id>UBERON:8600004</oboInOwl:id>
        <rdfs:comment>It is quite common to refer to visceral muscles as smooth muscles, by analogy with vertebrates; however, most visceral muscles in arthropods are actually striated.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>visceral muscle tissue</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
